description: A quest for better food led owners, Nathan White and William O'Donnell, to open their own food truck. Tired of the same old boring food options, they decided to specialize in making what they call "ECLECTIC COMFORT FOOD."The objective is to take foods everyone is familiar with, and give them a unique or eclectic spin which transforms the items from ordinary to extraordinary.The Hunger Squad Food Truck is now rolling throughout Ohio taming tormented tummies. We are Your Prescription for Hunger.We look forward to serving everyone our delicious food. Give us a try---we are confident you will enjoy it as much as we do!
name: Hunger Squad
